{"type":"message","id":"c7a821cd","parentId":"47b12970","timestamp":"2026-05-02T02:59:50.704Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby ran `xurl auth apps list` and I can see three apps registered:\n1. `default` - has client_id starting with \"YOUR_CLI...\"\n2. `my-app` - client_id starting with \"YOUR_CLI...\"\n3. `xai-prod` - client_id starting with \"WDNldnBy...\" (which looks like a real Base64-encoded ID)\n\nSo `xai-prod` IS registered with a real client ID. The issue is that `xurl auth oauth2` failed with \"something went wrong\".\n\nLet me help him troubleshoot. The issue might be:\n1. The OAuth flow itself failed (could be network, XAI service issue, etc.)\n\n\n2. The `xai-prod` app needs to be set as the default, or there could be a problem with the tokens themselves.\n\nLet me have him check the current auth status first to see what's actually happening.\n","thinkingSignature":"28f656c77cc82d2949af44e05ab72d86e9e355d6ba714b8aeba6c848cda99bae"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nGood — `xai-prod` IS registered with what looks like a real client ID (not the placeholder \"YOUR_CLI...\"). That's good progress!\n\n---\n\n## Let's see if it actually works\n\nRun this to check auth status:\n\n```bash\nxurl auth status\n```\n\nIf it says \"not authenticated\", then the OAuth flow needs to complete. But the issue is the OAuth failed.\n\n---\n\n## Try This Fix:\n\nFirst, set `xai-prod` as the default app, then run OAuth:\n\n```bash\nxurl auth default xai-prod\nxurl auth oauth2\n```\n\n---\n\n## If It Still Fails, Try With Username\n\n```bash\nxurl auth oauth2 --username bobbygalletta\n```\n\n(replace with your actual X handle without @)\n\n---\n\n## Also Check:\n\nTry running a simple read-only command:\n```bash\nxurl /2/users/me\n```\n\nIf that works → your auth IS working and it's just the OAuth browser flow that had an issue.\n\nIf it fails → we need to troubleshoot the auth token.\n\n---\n\n## What Do You See From:\n\n```bash\nxurl auth status\nxurl /2/users/me\n```\n\nPaste what you get and we'll know exactly where we stand! 🔧"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":36253,"output":447,"cacheRead":320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37020,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777690771948,"responseId":"06449b94006220d1cf8207f19e2c2ec5"}}
