{"type":"message","id":"83bb3e70","parentId":"3d19dc91","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:17:49.097Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"We just successfully posted a tweet! Agent X is working. Let me report back to Bobby with the good news and clean up the memory/conversation about the credentials since they're now set up.\n","thinkingSignature":"b49d9c2d1b56961cf6f7e85bbaacae55212809cbc8d0e8c8b01e03dde12ce689"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**AGENT X IS LIVE! 🚀**\n\nJust posted this from your account:\n\n> *\"Testing xurl from @BobbyGalletta's AI team - Agent X is now operational!\"*\n\n✅ `whoami` — working\n✅ `timeline` — working  \n✅ `post` — **working**\n\nYour X credentials are configured and Agent X can now:\n- Post, reply, quote\n- Search, timeline, mentions\n- Follow/unfollow, like/repost\n- DMs, media upload\n- Everything the skill supports\n\n---\n\n## What's Next?\n\n**Go delete that test tweet** from your profile, then let me know what you want Agent X to do! \n\nSome ideas:\n- Draft and schedule posts\n- Monitor mentions and engage\n- Search for topics you care about\n- Auto-repost/like content matching certain keywords\n- Build your following\n\nAgent X is your X/Twitter specialist on the team. What do you want to automate? 🐦"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":251,"output":239,"cacheRead":42048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42538,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777691861363,"responseId":"06449fd5e9f1e27aba3c0c172a33c2b3"}}
