{"type":"message","id":"bdfe4fb9","parentId":"9f585c6e","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:19:31.833Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is asking if Agent X can now read his X feed and post. Yes, xurl is configured and working. Let me confirm what Agent X can do now.\n","thinkingSignature":"cdfa459be2156727c9924ff29d61056765cdac4e9a0490be3b23366224d3cfd1"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nYes Bobby! Exactly.\n\n---\n\n## Agent X Capabilities\n\n**Reading:**\n- ✅ Home timeline\n- ✅ Mentions\n- ✅ User profile / who is who\n- ✅ Search posts\n- ✅ Followers / following lists\n- ✅ Bookmarks / likes\n\n**Writing:**\n- ✅ Post (text only)\n- ✅ Post with media (upload first, then attach)\n- ✅ Reply to any post\n- ✅ Quote repost\n- ✅ Like / unlike\n- ✅ Repost / undo repost\n- ✅ Follow / unfollow\n- ✅ Send DMs\n\n**Everything via xurl** — the same commands we just tested.\n\n---\n\n## How It Works\n\nAgent X (or me as Agent X) will run xurl commands directly on your Mac. Since we're authenticated as `BobbyGalletta`, it has full access to your account.\n\n---\n\n## Example Tasks for Agent X\n\n- \"Monitor my mentions and alert me\"\n- \"Search for AI agents content and summarize top posts\"\n- \"Post this thread about YouTube growth\"\n- \"Like all posts from Elon that mention AI\"\n- \"Reply to everyone who mentioned me today\"\n- \"Follow people who interact with my content\"\n\n---\n\n**Want me to do something specific with X right now?** I can test post, search, read — whatever you want to see work. 🐦"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":42379,"output":309,"cacheRead":128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42816,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777691958829,"responseId":"0644a037675072c57cb00cfde79740a9"}}
