{"type":"message","id":"96ab33b0","parentId":"8ee30284","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:23:59.577Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby says Agent X got the message and is now working. Great news! I should acknowledge this and maybe ask what Agent X is doing or if there's anything else we need to set up.\n","thinkingSignature":"ca5be88b7f624ae21cdb1366b5f4cecefa83cd2dba2446e6d12c00f302f3c0b7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nAwesome! 🎉 Agent X is officially online and ready to handle Twitter tasks.\n\n---\n\n## Quick Recap — What's Set Up\n\n| | |\n|---|---|\n| **xurl** | ✅ Installed + authenticated |\n| **Account** | @BobbyGalletta |\n| **Agent X** | ✅ Notified and operational |\n| **Posting/Reading** | ✅ Working |\n| **All xurl commands** | ✅ Ready to use |\n\n---\n\n## Agent X Can Now Handle Tasks Like:\n\n- Posting content for you\n- Monitoring mentions\n- Searching topics\n- Engaging (likes, reposts, follows)\n- Auto-scheduling\n- Building your following\n\n---\n\n**Anything else you want to set up for the team?** \n\nWe just knocked out:\n1. ✅ Local model advice (Mac Mini planning)\n2. ✅ X/Twitter integration (Agent X)\n\nWhat's next on your list? 🛠️"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":44251,"output":226,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44733,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777692229524,"responseId":"0644a14648357da7184f041ecdb47cdd"}}
